4) WAP to create multiple child processes using fork().
A- import os
for i in range(3):
    pid = os.fork()
    if pid == 0:
        print("Child", i+1, "PID:", os.getpid())
        break

O/P:
Child 1 PID: 1234
Child 2 PID: 1235
Child 3 PID: 1236
