5) WAP to create a child process using fork() & display the process IDs of both parent & child using getpid() & getppid().
A- import os
pid = os.fork()
if pid == 0:
    print("Child PID:", os.getpid())
    print("Parent PID from child:", os.getppid())
else:
    print("Parent PID:", os.getpid())

O/P:
Parent PID: 1233
Child PID: 1234
Parent PID from child: 1233
